'From Squeak3.8alpha of ''17 July 2004'' [latest update: #5976] on 18 August 2004 at 3:30:09 pm'!!TextMorphEditor methodsFor: 'typing support' stamp: 'yo 8/18/2004 15:29'!dispatchOnCharacter: char with: typeAheadStream	"Carry out the action associated with this character, if any.	Type-ahead is passed so some routines can flush or use it."	| ret |	((char == Character cr) and: [morph acceptOnCR])		ifTrue:			[sensor keyboard.  "Gobble cr -- probably unnecessary."			self closeTypeIn.			^ true].	ret _ super dispatchOnCharacter: char with: typeAheadStream.	morph updateFromParagraph.	^ ret.! !